select distinct
claim_analyst_identifier,
claim_analyst_rut_num,
analyst_profile_description,
analyst_name,
rec_crt_dtm,
max_sid,
src_sys_cd
from
(SELECT
src.claim_analyst_identifier,
src.claim_analyst_rut_num,
src.analyst_profile_description,
translate(src.analyst_name,'#','') as analyst_name,
src.rec_crt_dtm,
src.src_sys_cd,
1 AS DUMMY,
ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY src.claim_analyst_identifier,src.src_sys_cd,src.analyst_profile_description ORDER BY src.rec_crt_dtm DESC ) AS RNK
from
(select  
distinct 
CAST(p.SPERSON AS INTEGER) as claim_analyst_identifier
,CAST(p.NNUMNIF AS VARCHAR(35)) as claim_analyst_rut_num
,CAST('Claim Analyst' AS VARCHAR(80)) as analyst_profile_description
,CAST(p.tbuscar AS VARCHAR(100)) as analyst_name
,CAST('axis' AS VARCHAR(10)) as src_sys_cd
,p.rec_crt_dtm as rec_crt_dtm
from cdp_ods.sisaxis_siniestros s 
inner join cdp_ods.sisaxis_tramitadores t
on s.CTRAMIT = t.CTRAMIT
inner join cdp_stg_dwh.sisaxis_personas p
on t.SPERSON = p.SPERSON

union
 
select
distinct  
CAST(p.SPERSON AS INTEGER) as claim_analyst_identifier
,CAST(p.NNUMNIF AS VARCHAR(35)) as analyst_rut_number
,CAST('Spare Parts Analyst' AS VARCHAR(80)) as analyst_profile_description
,CAST(p.tbuscar AS VARCHAR(100)) as claim_analyst_name
,CAST('axis' AS VARCHAR(10)) as src_sys_cd
,u.rec_crt_dtm as rec_crt_dtm
from 
cdp_stg_dwh.sisaxis_usuarios u
inner join cdp_ods.sissiniestro_sin_autoriza_ordenes a
on a.usuario_autoriza = u.CUSUARI
inner join 
cdp_ods.sisaxis_personas p
on u.SPERSON = p.SPERSON 
 )src
)main_src
LEFT JOIN (SELECT 1 as DUMMY, max(dim_claim_analyst_key) AS MAX_SID from cdp_dwh.dim_claim_analyst_t) LKP_TGT
ON LKP_TGT.DUMMY=main_src.DUMMY
WHERE main_src.RNK =1;
